    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This dependable vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some character through honest cosmetic wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a solid and functional choice that gets the job done. It's the perfect opportunity to own a well-running car at a great value\u2014ideal for anyone seeking practical transportation with plenty of life left in it!",
