      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle maintained to an impeccable standard that rivals its original showroom debut. This specimen boasts a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, untouched condition. Meticulously serviced and handled with the utmost care, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a vehicle in its most refined state. Experience the confidence of a machine that defines the gold standard of pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
